<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Verify Your Email Address - Event Manager</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #3B82F6;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .verification-box {
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #3B82F6;
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #2563EB;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .warning {
            background-color: #FEE2E2;
            border-left: 4px solid #EF4444;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .code-block {
            background-color: #F3F4F6;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #D1D5DB;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>üìß Verify Your Email Address</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{ user.firstName ?? 'there' }}!</h2>
        
        <p>Thank you for registering with <strong>Event Manager</strong>! To complete your registration and activate your account, please verify your email address.</p>
        
        <div class="verification-box">
            <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Action Required</h3>
            <p><strong>Your account is currently inactive.</strong> You must verify your email address before you can log in and access Event Manager features.</p>
        </div>
        
        <h3>Verify Your Email</h3>
        <p>Click the button below to verify your email address and activate your account:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ verificationUrl }}" class="button">
                ‚úÖ Verify Email Address
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If the button doesn't work, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
        <div class="code-block">
            {{ verificationUrl }}
        </div>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <h4>‚è∞ Important:</h4>
            <p>This verification link will expire on <strong>{{ expiresAt|date('F j, Y \\a\\t g:i A') }}</strong> (24 hours from registration).</p>
            <p>If the link expires, you can request a new verification email.</p>
        </div>
        
        <h3>What happens after verification?</h3>
        <p>Once you verify your email, you'll be able to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>üîê Log in to your Event Manager account</li>
            <li>üéØ Browse and register for events</li>
            <li>üë• Connect with other event attendees</li>
            <li>üé™ Create and manage your own events</li>
            <li>üìù Participate in discussions and comments</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h3>Didn't register?</h3>
        <p>If you didn't create an account with Event Manager, please ignore this email. No account will be activated without email verification.</p>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The Event Manager Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This verification email was sent to <strong>{{ user.email }}</strong> because someone registered for an Event Manager account with this email address.</p>
        <p>Event Manager - Making events accessible to everyone</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
